13 SECTION 2. Said section 4 of said chapter 94G of the General Laws, as appearing in the
14 2020 Official Edition, is hereby amended by striking in line 258 after the word "unless" the
15 following:- "at least 85 per cent of the audience is reasonably expected to be 21 years of age or
16 older, as determined by reliable, up-to-date audience composition data" and inserting in place
